{"id": "1408497210504511488", "channel_id": "1400749543288475770", "type": 0, "author_id": "693983290423509042", "author_name": "climbkaly", "author_bot": false, "content": "So you can make the best counter N team.\n\nDaffodil / gDoll / Horla / Nautila \n\nPut horla in joy\n\nExalt daff choose 2 cost\n\nPlay those cards get high temp counter\n\nExalt Nautila", "timestamp": "2025-08-22T17:05:03.597000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
