{"id": "1408511740320288768", "channel_id": "1400749543288475770", "type": 19, "author_id": "452731110556696596", "author_name": "aurora3981", "author_bot": false, "content": "Imo the biggest issue is you're not abusing the chapter gimmick. After beating thais you have unlocked the dupe gimmick which corpo hameln and more awakers can abuse.\nI'll list the 3 strongest cheese strategy you can do atm.\n- just dupe hameln 3 cost for arithmetica and draw then loop through your whole deck turn 1\nSimple and effective\n- hameln + horla joy + karen wheel + prototype battery relic\nThe most powerful but needs a bit of rng, same strategy as the one I mentioned before but you don't spend your arithmetica. Instead you hoard as many arithmetica as possible. Karen wheel healing is uncapped so you can heal for 800 hp per exalt for example. Then prototype battery relic will give you enough aliemus for overexalt every turn.\n- dupe corpo 4 cost\nFar faster than hameln cheese, you dupe corpo 4 cost then discard it multiple times via lily posse / corpo exalt / aurita 2 cost. Once you beat N you unlock joy orison, put it on aurita 2 cost to discard 2 times", "timestamp": "2025-08-22T18:02:47.775000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["716978977117306931"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1408490157426081832", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1408512511900123136", "channel_id": "1400749543288475770", "type": 0, "author_id": "452731110556696596", "author_name": "aurora3981", "author_bot": false, "content": "Wait there's an even more direct approach, dupe gelot 1 cost aoe. Just punch enemy in the face directly with the usual gelot team.", "timestamp": "2025-08-22T18:05:51.734000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1408513386441998398", "channel_id": "1400749543288475770", "type": 0, "author_id": "452731110556696596", "author_name": "aurora3981", "author_bot": false, "content": "You have far better dps options than rat like doresain / gelot / 24 / corpo. All can be their own team", "timestamp": "2025-08-22T18:09:20.241000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
